description: Sample Redis Command-to-API Mapping (first 5 commands, 3 clients)

sample_commands.name: ACL
sample_commands.summary: A container for Access List Control commands.

sample_commands.name: ACL CAT
sample_commands.summary: Lists the ACL categories, or the commands inside a category.

sample_commands.name: ACL DELUSER
sample_commands.summary: Deletes ACL users, and terminates their connections.

sample_commands.name: ACL DRYRUN
sample_commands.summary: Simulates the execution of a command by a user, without executing the command.

sample_commands.name: ACL GENPASS
sample_commands.summary: Generates a pseudorandom, secure password that can be used to identify ACL users.
